McLain talk sey di toy making unit gree to buy Buddy L Corp, wey be one line of toy cars, and toy accessories.

Di price no be official announcement, but one executive of LJN Toys Ltd, MCA unit yarn sey di closely held Buddy L get annual sales of over $20 million a year.

Di 40 years old Buddy L concern, base on di New York area, dey design and develop toys under di name Buddy L, and my first Buddy.

McLain talk sey e dey expect di proposed transaction to complete no later than Nov. 10.

